OL,6,FMen also tend to lead in negotiations,
OL,7,Fwith 36% taking charge of the house
OL,8,Fprice negotiations compared with 20%
OL,9,Fof women.
OL,11,FWomen are more likely to voice a
OL,12,Fdislike or reject a property (57%
OL,13,Fversus 43%) than men, the research
OL,14,Ffound.
OL,16,FWhen it comes to making compromises,
OL,17,F31% of men feel they more frequently
OL,18,Fmake concessions, versus 25% of women.
