OL,6,FZoopla commissioned Opinium to survey
OL,7,F2,000 adults across the UK in July and
OL,8,FAugust who live with someone else in
OL,9,Ftheir household and have made at least
OL,10,Fone house move.
OL,12,FDaniel Copley, a consumer expert at
OL,13,FZoopla, said: "For a significant
OL,14,Fportion of the market, the family home
OL,15,Fis truly a family decision.
OL,16,FUnderstanding these nuanced dynamics
OL,17,Fis invaluable and it underscores the
OL,18,Fimportance of open communication for a
OL,19,Fsmoother, happier house hunt."
