OL,6,F"Therefore, it is positive to see that
OL,7,Fthe children of many families are
OL,8,Fplaying a key role in the final
OL,9,Fdecision-making process for their next
OL,10,Ffamily home, which is more likely to
OL,11,Flead to a happier and more successful
OL,12,Ffuture for everyone involved.
OL,14,F"Personally, in my professional
OL,15,Fopinion, I have noted that women tend
OL,16,Fto lead the general home buying and
OL,17,Fselling process."
